  "text": "Martin developed the HOS in the United States of America (USA) in 2005 to assess patients with acetabular labral tears who were physically active, young, or both [CITATION_1] . The instrument was validated using two groups: individuals receiving hip arthroscopy and those with acetabular labral tears [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
